# x86 BOF loader DLL — i386 PE with relocations preserved, embedded
# via go:embed so `go build` works without mingw32. Rebuild via
# scripts/build-bof-x86-loader.sh (host i686-w64-mingw32 or Podman).
!runtime/bof/internal/x86loader/bof_x86_loader.x86.dll
